ARCTIC.
RADIO SERVICES.
1. A S1 SOLAR RADIATION STORM HAS BEGUN. THIS
   COULD HAVE A MINOR IMPACT ON HF RADIO
   COMMUNICATIONS IN THE POLAR REGIONS FOR THE
   NEXT 24 HOURS.
2. TUNE INTO RADIO STATION WWV OR WWVB FOR MORE
   INFORMATION. SEE NGA PUBLICATION 117, RADIO
   BROADCAST SIGNALS FOR STATION INFORMATION.
3. CANCEL THIS MSG 272300Z NOV.
